org.apache.cayenne.query

Class NamedQuery

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.cayenne.query.IndirectQuery
      • org.apache.cayenne.query.NamedQuery
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Query
    Deprecated. 
    since 4.0 you should use MappedSelect or MappedExec instead.

    @Deprecated
public class NamedQuery
extends IndirectQuery
    A query that is a reference to a named parameterized query stored in the mapping. The actual query is resolved during execution.
    Since:
    1.2
    See Also:
